    public static class SimplexStream.Head
extends java.lang.Object
    A Head provides the FO part of a FIFO queue when attached to a Tail to which simplices have been enqueued.

      • lessThan

        public boolean lessThan(SimplexStream.Head q)
        Compare one Head to another.

        This is a very fast comparison that will only work if both Head instances are heads for the same Tail.

        Parameters:
        q - Head to compare
        Returns:
        true if this is prior to q, else false.
